Anitra Ford https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anitra_Ford 0 Anitra Ford (born 1942) is an American former actress and model. She is best known for her work as a model on the game show The Price Is Right. She has also appeared in movies such as The Big Bird Cage (1972), Invasion of the Bee Girls (1973), and The Longest Yard (1974), as well as in episodes of the television programs Banacek, S.W.A.T., Mannix and Starsky and Hutch.
